Class SPCSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • tool.SPCSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TupleSet<Element>

    public class SPCSet
extends java.lang.Object
implements TupleSet<Element>
    Class for the sigma/problem/constraint sets. Now the name is also a shortcut for SolvingProximityConstraints. Basically a facade for ArrayList<Tuple<Element>>
    Version:
    1.1
    Author:
    Jan-Michael Holzinger
